    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙反对少数党政府预算案通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/portugal-s-opposition-to-let-minority-government-s-budget-pass</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙最大的反对党表示，计划让2025年预算提案在议会获得通过，这是该国少数派政府生存的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/portugal-s-opposition-to-let-minority-government-s-budget-pass</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 19:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥宣扬民主党全国代表大会将产生 3.71 亿美元影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chicago-touts-371-million-impact-from-democratic-convention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据芝加哥市营销部门称，民主党全国代表大会给芝加哥带来的经济总效益约为 3.71 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chicago-touts-371-million-impact-from-democratic-convention</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 19:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯简史：又一位领导人倒台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/what-is-hamas-what-does-it-want-who-will-lead-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年 10 月 7 日，巴勒斯坦伊斯兰组织哈马斯对以色列发动了规模空前的袭击，挑起了一场新的重大战争。致力于摧毁以色列的哈马斯自 2007 年以来一直统治着加沙地带，这是一个孤立的地中海飞地，居住着 220 万巴勒斯坦人。美国和欧盟将其列为恐怖组织，其自杀式爆炸和其他针对以色列人的袭击是导致以色列与哈马斯对手之间和平谈判破裂的一个因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/what-is-hamas-what-does-it-want-who-will-lead-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称辛瓦尔之死为结束加沙战争提供了“机会”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/harris-says-sinwar-s-death-offers-opportunity-to-end-gaza-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯表示，哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔的死提供了“最终结束加沙战争的机会”，并表示此次击毙辛瓦尔将使以色列更加安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/harris-says-sinwar-s-death-offers-opportunity-to-end-gaza-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:28:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利反犯罪策划者因强奸指控辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chile-anti-crime-mastermind-steps-down-following-rape-allegation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利内政部副部长曼努埃尔·蒙萨尔维 (Manuel Monsalve) 因涉嫌强奸而接受调查的报道发布后辞职，这一令人震惊的进展导致政府失去了一位顶级打击犯罪的官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chile-anti-crime-mastermind-steps-down-following-rape-allegation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>四位部长计划离职，特鲁多将改组内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/trudeau-to-shuffle-cabinet-as-four-ministers-plan-departures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于一些部长决定不参加下次选举，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多将在未来几周内改组内阁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/trudeau-to-shuffle-cabinet-as-four-ministers-plan-departures</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳执政党新爱国党因议员叛逃失去议会多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/ghana-opposition-now-majority-in-parliament-as-mps-vacate-seats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳执政党新爱国党的部分议员决定改变自己的地位，导致其失去了议会多数席位，导致该党在本来就悬而未决的议会中席位数量进一步减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/ghana-opposition-now-majority-in-parliament-as-mps-vacate-seats</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 17:51:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔已被击毙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/israel-s-foreign-minister-katz-says-hamas-chief-sinwar-killed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列士兵杀死了 10 月 7 日袭击事件的主谋、哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔。他的死给该激进组织高层留下了一个巨大空缺，并促使美国再次向总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡施压，要求其结束加沙地带的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/israel-s-foreign-minister-katz-says-hamas-chief-sinwar-killed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 16:46:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼敦促欧洲领导人加强移民规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/eu-summit-meloni-pushes-europe-to-get-tougher-on-migrants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着各国面临政治压力，要求减少移民人数，欧洲领导人开始制定更为严格的移民政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/eu-summit-meloni-pushes-europe-to-get-tougher-on-migrants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 13:14:37 GMT</pubDate>
